1:1 COMMENT "# borrowed_record.z -- Class with .lock field outside the iterator pattern"
1:75 EOL "\n"
2:1 COMMENT "#"
2:2 EOL "\n"
3:1 COMMENT "# Demonstrates a \"view\" or \"slice\" type: a small stack-allocated class"
3:71 EOL "\n"
4:1 COMMENT "# that holds a locked reference to another object's private data. The"
4:70 EOL "\n"
5:1 COMMENT "# view is locked against the source for its lifetime; when the view falls"
5:74 EOL "\n"
6:1 COMMENT "# out of scope, the source is unlocked."
6:40 EOL "\n"
7:1 EOL "\n"
8:1 COMMENT "# A small container with three named coordinates."
8:50 EOL "\n"
